data.title: A premier natural gas midstream operator in the Marcellus & Utica shale.
data.text:
On July 22, 2024, Equitrans Midstream Corporation was acquired by EQT Corporation. During the transition process, there are often questions that arise from various stakeholders – please use the information below for assistance:

Investors: Visit EQT’s investor website for contact information, as well as annual reports, analyst presentations, and earnings releases.

Customers: Equitrans Midstream customers can continue to access informational postings for our interstate transmission and gathering facilities on the Equitrans Customer Portal

Property Owners: Contact the EQT Community Relations team by using the EQT Contact Us form or calling 844-EQT-LAND (844-378-5263).

Vendors/Suppliers: For additional information regarding procurement services, please email: currentvendorrelations@eqt.com

Foundation and Local Giving: For more information on funding priorities and to submit requests, visit the EQT Foundation page or contact Ellen Rossi at erossi@eqt.com

Media Inquiries: Visit EQT Media for access to the latest news and information about our company. All additional media inquiries can be directed to Courtney Loper at courtney.loper@eqt.com

All other inquiries can be submitted on the EQT Contact Us form.
